column2: ALPHA BLACK TO BRAVO BLACK. DO YOU COPY. OVER.
THIS IS ALPHA BLACK CALLING BRAVO BLACK. DO YOU COPY. PLEASE RESPOND. OVER.
THIS IS ALPHA. WE ARE APPROACHING FROM YOU NOW ON SOUTH WEST. HOLD YOU FIRE ON SOUTH WEST. ACKNOWLEDGE. OVER.
ALPHA TO BRAVO. DO YOU KIDD AROUND. WE ARE APPROACHING FROM YOU ON SOUTH WEST. DO YOU COPY SOUTH WEST. OVER.
ALPHA TO BRAVO. ARE YOU SURE. REPEAT WHAT IS OUR BEARING TO YOUR POSITION. OVER.
ALPHA TO BRAVO. GOOD. MAKE SURE YOU REMEMBER THAT. WE ARE COMING IN. OVER.
ALPHA BLACK TO PAPA BEAR. WE HAVE REACHED THE BRAVOS POSITION. MISSION ACCOMPLISHED. OVER.
BRAVO BLACK COPIES. HEARING YOU LOUD AND CLEAR. OVER.
BRAVO TO ALPHA. CAN YOU REPEAT WHAT DIRECTION WAS THAT AGAIN. OVER.
UH OK BRAVO COPIES SOUTH WEST. OVER.
BRAVO TO ALPHA. WE COPY YOU ARE APPROACHING FROM SOUTH WEST. WE ARE HOLDING OUR FIRE TO SOUTH WEST. OVER.
PAPA BEAR TO ALPHA. GOOD WORK OVER THERE. OVER.
